  "title": "Associate Engineer (Electrical / East)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Lead the integration and implementation of hardware and software engineering systems</li>\n  <li>Plan, manage, and supervise project execution with thorough QA and technical validation</li>\n  <li>Oversee program change management, hardware deployment, and ensure proper documentation</li>\n  <li>Design, program, and implement PLC/SCADA systems from concept to completion</li>\n  <li>Develop system interfaces between PLC and SCADA platforms</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with clients, prepare progress reports, and maintain project documentation</li>\n  <li>Perform independent troubleshooting and on-site technical support</li>\n  <li>Must possess a valid Class 3 driving license</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
